          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-Cross section measurement for Hg-199(n,n')Hg-199-m",
                " reaction from 0.78 to 6.3 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "VDG"
                ],
                "institute": "2JPNJAE"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " 5.5 MV Van de Graaff"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-D"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " A deuterium target supplied by the",
                " Radiochemical Centre was used. By cooling the target",
                " with a jet of air, no appreciable decrease in neutron",
                " yield was observed for 20 hr with a beam current up",
                " to about 2 micro-A in a 20 mm2 spot."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "P-LI7"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " A Li target was prepared by the vacuum",
                " evaporation method of natural lithium fluoride LiF",
                " onto a Ti backing foil. The thickness, of the lithium",
                " fluoride layer is about 500 mu-g/cm2 which corresponds",
                " to an energy loss of about 60 keV for 2 MeV protons."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Mercury sulphate powder pressed into discs of",
                " 20 milli-m diameter and about 3 milli-m thick,",
                " weighed to 1.0 milli-g.",
                ".Samples sandwiched by indium foils of the same",
                " diameter and of 0.5 milli-m thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Activation techniques."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A high purity germanium detector of diameter",
                "  42.5 milli-m and length 59.9 milli-m used to measure",
                "  gamma activity."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SIBAR",
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A proton recoil telescope",
                "  consisting of a polythene radiator in front of a",
                "  proton detector:",
                "    * above 5 MeV neutron energy a silicon surface",
                "          barrier detector",
                "    * below 5 MeV a CsI(Tl) detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "PART-DET": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DG"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  Decay gammas"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "N"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "   neutrons"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Self absorption of the gamma rays in the Hg sample",
                " were calculated by a monte carlo method. The self",
                " absorption in the indium foils was less than 1%."
              ]
            }
          ],
